== 效能指標 ==
* BFE，[[細菌過濾率|細菌過濾率]]（Bacterial Filtration Efficiency）：一般使用3μm大小的粒子测量<ref name=med>{{cite web |last1=Robertson |first1=Paddy |title=Comparison of Mask Standards, Ratings, and Filtration Effectiveness |url=https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/comparison-mask-standards-rating-effectiveness/ |website=Smart Air Filters |date=15 March 2020 |accessdate=2020-04-30 |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711203308/https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/comparison-mask-standards-rating-effectiveness/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* PFE，[[粒子過濾率|粒子過濾率]]（Particulate Filtration Efficiency）：医用情况下一般使用0.1μm大小的粒子测量，<ref name=med/>其他[[自吸过滤式呼吸器|自吸过滤式呼吸器]]使用最不易过滤的0.3μm<ref name="tsi">{{cite web |author1=TSI Incorporated |title=Mechanisms of Filtration for High Efficiency Fibrous Filters - Application Note ITI-041 |url=https://www.tsi.com/getmedia/4982cf03-ea99-4d0f-a660-42b24aedba14/ITI-041-A4?ext=.pdf |accessdate=29 April 2020 |archive-date=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516185154/https://www.tsi.com/getmedia/4982cf03-ea99-4d0f-a660-42b24aedba14/ITI-041-A4?ext=.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* VFE，[[病毒過濾率|病毒過濾率]]（Viral Filtration Efficiency）：一般也使用3μm大小的粒子测量<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rengasamy |first1=S |last2=Shaffer |first2=R |last3=Williams |first3=B |last4=Smit |first4=S |title=A comparison of facemask and respirator filtration test methods. |journal=Journal of occupational and environmental hygiene |date=2017-02 |volume=14 |issue=2 |pages=92-103 |doi=10.1080/15459624.2016.1225157 |pmid=27540979 |pmc=7157953}}</ref>

